sequenceDiagram
  participant TC as Seata TC
  participant O as mall-order
  participant ODB as mall_order DB
  participant I as mall-inventory
  participant IDB as mall_inventory DB

  O->>TC: 开启 create-order 全局事务
  O->>I: lock(orderNo, skuId, quantity)
  I->>IDB: 更新 available / locked
  I-->>O: 库存锁定成功
  O->>ODB: 写入 order_info / order_item

  alt 订单与库存操作全部成功
    O->>TC: 提交全局事务
    TC-->>O: 提交完成
  else 任一步发生异常
    O->>TC: 请求回滚
    TC->>ODB: 回滚订单写入
    TC->>IDB: 回滚库存锁定
    TC-->>O: 返回业务失败
  end
